@startuml CoreNeedleBiopsy_Workflow_GroupedOrder
title Szenario 6: Gruppierter Auftrag\nCore Needle Biopsy – Histologie + Molekularpathologie

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #555555
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #555555
skinparam sequenceGroupBorderColor #AAAAAA
skinparam sequenceGroupFontSize 11
skinparam noteFontSize 10
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF8DC

participant "**Placer (KIS)**\nUrologie" as Placer #BDD7EE
participant "**Filler (LIS)**\nPathologie" as Filler #C6EFCE

== Auftragserstellung (2024-01-15, 08:00) ==

Placer -> Filler : POST Bundle (type: **transaction**)\n  Patient\n  ServiceRequest-A (Histologie,\n    requisition: **G24-001**)\n  ServiceRequest-B (BRCA1/2-Panel,\n    requisition: **G24-001**)\n  Specimen [x12] (status: **available**)\n  Task-A (requested, focus: SR-A)\n  Task-B (requested, focus: SR-B)
activate Filler
Filler --> Placer : Bundle (type: **transaction-response**)\n  201 Created
deactivate Filler

note over Placer, Filler : **Zwei Tasks mit gemeinsamer Requisition**\nTask-A: Histologie\nTask-B: Molekularpathologie (BRCA1/2)

== Annahme beider Auftraege (2024-01-15, 14:00) ==

Filler -> Placer : PUT Task-A (status: **accepted**)
Filler -> Placer : PUT Task-B (status: **accepted**)

== Parallele Bearbeitung ==

Filler -> Placer : PUT Task-A (status: **in-progress**)
Filler -> Placer : PUT Task-B (status: **in-progress**)

note over Filler : Beide Auftraege laufen\nparallel aber unabhaengig

group Histologie [Task-A, 3-5 Tage]
  Filler -> Filler : Makroskopie
  Filler -> Filler : Mikroskopie (HE)
  Filler -> Filler : Diagnostische Schlussfolgerung
end

group Molekularpathologie [Task-B, 7-14 Tage]
  Filler -> Filler : DNA-Extraktion\n(aus Tumor-positivem Block)
  Filler -> Filler : NGS-Panel BRCA1/2
  Filler -> Filler : Befundung Varianten
end

== Histologie abgeschlossen (2024-01-20) ==

Filler -> Placer : POST Bundle (type: **document**, signed)\n  DiagnosticReport-A (status: **final**)\n  Histologie-Befund
activate Placer
Placer --> Filler : 201 Created
deactivate Placer

Filler -> Placer : PUT Task-A\n(status: **completed**\noutput: Bundle-A)
activate Placer
Placer --> Filler : 200 OK
deactivate Placer

note over Placer, Filler : **Task-A: completed**\nHistologie fertig.\nTask-B laeuft noch.

Placer -> Placer : ServiceRequest-A\n(status: **completed**)

== Molekularpathologie abgeschlossen (2024-01-29) ==

Filler -> Placer : POST Bundle (type: **document**, signed)\n  DiagnosticReport-B (status: **final**)\n  BRCA1/2-Befund
activate Placer
Placer --> Filler : 201 Created
deactivate Placer

Filler -> Placer : PUT Task-B\n(status: **completed**\noutput: Bundle-B)
activate Placer
Placer --> Filler : 200 OK
deactivate Placer

note over Placer, Filler : **Task-B: completed**\nBeide Auftraege abgeschlossen.

Placer -> Placer : ServiceRequest-B\n(status: **completed**)

note over Placer : Beide Befunde im KIS:\n- Histologie: Gleason 4+3=7\n- MolPath: BRCA2 pathogen\n\nTherapieentscheidung:\nOlaparib-Indikation pruefen

@enduml
